                Ordinance, the expression
                    <term class="old_format"><b><i>machinery
                            or
                plant</i></b></term>
                    (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">機械或工業裝置</term>) shall include or be deemed to
                include the items specified in the second column of the First Part of the Table
                annexed to this rule but not the items specified in the second column of the Second
                Part of that Table which shall be deemed to be included in the expression
                    <term class="old_format"><b><i>any
                            implement, utensil and
                article</i></b></term>
                    (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">任何工具</term>、<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">器具及物品</term>) for the purposes of the Ordinance.</def></subsection><subsection id="ID_1438410935109_004" name="2" temporalId="s2_2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content>The rates of depreciation specified in the third column of the First Part of
                the Table annexed to this rule are hereby prescribed for the purpose of ascertaining
                the annual allowance to be made under <ref>sections 37(2)</ref>, <ref>37A(2)</ref>
                and <ref>39B(3)</ref> of the Ordinance.<inline class="width_3"> </inline><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1980/ln365">L.N. 365 of
                    1980</ref>)</sourceNote></content></subsection><subsection id="ID_1438410935109_012" name="3" temporalId="s2_3"><num value="3">(3)</num><def name="PlantOrMachinery">Wharves shall not be or be deemed to be included in the
                expression
                    <term class="old_format"><b><i>plant
                            or
                machinery</i></b></term>
                    (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">工業裝置或機械</term>) but where a balancing allowance or
                a balancing charge falls to be made to or on any person under <ref>section 35</ref>
                of the Ordinance in respect of any wharf, the allowances, if any, granted in respect
                of such wharf under <ref>section 37</ref> or <ref>37A</ref> of the Ordinance for any
                year of assessment prior to the year of assessment commencing on 1 April 1965, shall
                be taken into account in calculating such balancing allowance or charge.</def></subsection><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1965/ln101">L.N. 101 of
